# Scopa

http://scopa-front-end.herokuapp.com/

<img width="1440" alt="Screen Shot 2021-04-15 at 7 16 14 PM" src="https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/78765141/114949486-2103bd00-9e1f-11eb-9c24-a0f24ca209f5.png">

## Description:

Scopa is a class Italian cardgame. This app will allow for two players to enjoy from the same device.

## Tech:

 - React
 - React Hooks
 - CSS
 - AJAX
 - [Deckofcards API] (https://deckofcardsapi.com/)

## Features:

 - Users can enjoy a 2-player game of scopa
 - Users can view game score history

## Future Updates:

 - socket.io will be used to facilitate games from different clients
 - Logins will allow game history to be updated with user names
